  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Slice the whole wheat bread into 1-inch thick slices.",
    "Place the bread slices on a baking sheet and toast in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "While the bread is toasting, mix minced garlic with 1 tablespoon of chopped capers.",
    "When the bread is done toasting, remove it from the oven and drizzle with olive oil.",
    "Sprinkle the garlic caper mixture over the toasted bread slices.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve immediately."
